如果你是要驗證這批客戶在兩張表的風險等級是否一致，可以直接帶出欄位比較：

WITH CUST_LIST AS
(
    SELECT TS_CUST_ID
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO
    WHERE CUST_RE_NO_FLG = '1'
    EXCEPT
    SELECT TS_CUST_ID
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO
    WHERE CUST_RE_NO_FLG IN ('2','3')
)
SELECT
    c.TS_CUST_ID,
    b.HIGHRISK AS SRC_HIGHRISK,
    v.HIGHRISK AS VERIFY_HIGHRISK
FROM CUST_LIST c
INNER JOIN BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT b
    ON c.TS_CUST_ID = b.CustomerNo
INNER JOIN VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT v
    ON c.TS_CUST_ID = v.CustomerNo
WHERE ISNULL(b.HIGHRISK,'') <> ISNULL(v.HIGHRISK,'');

這樣會直接抓出 這批純 Flag=1 客戶中，來源與驗證環境 HIGHRISK 不一致的人。如果你是在做 AML 資轉驗證，這個通常比較有價值。